title: Owen Heap’s CV
text:
Data Science Student | Aspiring Data Analyst

ooheap@gmail.com | LinkedIn



Seeking data science internships and entry-level opportunities



Data analysis with Python
SQL database querying
Data visualization (Tableau)
Statistical modeling





Transforming raw data into actionable insights
Creating intuitive data visualizations
Developing predictive models
Business intelligence applications





2024 - Present Brigham Young University - Idaho - Bachelor of Science in Data Science (In progress) - Coursework: Statistics, Machine Learning, Data Wrangling
2021 Palomar College - General Studies




Languages: Python (Pandas, NumPy), SQL
Visualization: Tableau, Matplotlib, Seaborn
Tools: Jupyter Notebooks, Git, Excel
Concepts: Regression analysis, Data cleaning, ETL processes




Academic projects available upon request




Enthusiastic data science student looking to apply academic knowledge to real-world data challenges. Eager to contribute analytical skills while continuing to learn from industry professionals.
